item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

if(command.startsWith(“jail”){
String[] args = command.split(" ");
for (Player c2 : Player Variable) {
if (c2 != null) {
if(c2 = args[1]){
((Client Variable) c2).isJailed = true;
((Client Variable) c2).sendMessage(“You’re jailed”);
}
}
}
}
